songs.title: Don Quan Intro (2017)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Hey, man what the hell goin' on? It's your boy Don Quan, I'm back again, you know?
Like I said, we killed you with the Pimpin' Ain't Easy, then with the Glocks and Thots
Now with the SANDAS, suck a nigga dick or somethin' again, you know?
Just 'cause we on the album, ho
And we got the bonus tracks on there for the nasty ho, you know? (Believe it)
All that type of Squigin'
That boy T3 got a nigga like, he, like he on that pink Molly, haha (Haha)
Squig it up
